PRGM beta 0.0.3 for Aleph

install/filecopy to SD-CARD (ALEPH):
aleph-prgm.hex -> ALEPH/app/
aleph-prgm.ldr -> ALEPH/mod/
aleph-prgm.dsc -> ALEPH/mod/

REBOOT with aleph-prgm.hex



GLOBAL controls
sw2                 play step
sw3                 edit step+1
sw4                 page select

I/O
cv input0           play step +1
cv out0-3           cv!
audio out0-3        audio!
foot1               play step+1
foot2               play return to 1

page PARAM
parameters

page CURVE
encoders            trig
encoders + sw0      curve/mode
encoders + sw1      time



sound examples @ https://soundcloud.com/epla